The Telegraph - Calcutta
		 Friday, November 14, 2003  Field day for Daniel, Amyn 
 BY STAR RACER				 	 AmynAmyn Merchant on Red Chief (left) winning the Hilliard Cup from Aiberni at the RCTC on Thursday. Pictures by Kishor Roychowdhury				 										Calcutta: Trainer Daniel David and his stable jockey Amyn Merchant made a clean sweep of Thursdays six-event card. The duo not only lifted the 1,400m Hilliard Cup through their classic hope Red Chief, they also went on to strike quadruple of wins apiece.				 										Red Chief apart, Merchant also helped Daniels favourites, King Nicholas and Far Hope, win their respective events. Daniels fourth winner, Terrificco  a rank outsider in the Wiseman Cup  was, however, partnered by Md Amil.				 										Earlier in the afternoon, riding a well-judged race, Merchant had booted home trainer Errol Bhungards Gallant Romeo in the Salvage Handicap.				 										RESULTS				 										1. Nikita Handicap 1,200m: (5-4-3-1) Starry Man (Rabani) 1; Assailer (Surender) 2; April Ace (Melvyn) 3; Actualite (M. Reuben) 4. Won by: 5-1/4; 3/4; 1-3/4; (1-16.3). Tote: Win Rs 109; Place: 28; 25; Quinella: 246; Shp: 49; Tanala: 3,313. Fav: Actualite (1). Winner trained by Bharath S.				 										2. High Born Handicap 1,400m: (6-5-7-4) King Nicholas (Merchant) 1; Capistrano (Surjeet) 2; Flinders (A. P. Singh) 3; Smart Romeo (Salim) 4. Won by: 3/4; 2-1/4; 2-1/4; (1-30.5). Tote: Win Rs 20; Place: 11; 13; 18; Quinella: 26; Shp: 55; Tanala: 149. Fav: King Nicholas (6). Winner trained by Daniel D.				 										3. Salvage Handicap 1,100m: (2-4-1-5) Gallant Romeo (Merchant) 1; Pearl Dragon (Yasin) 2; Common Spirit (Jaiswal) 3; Moira (M. Reu ben) 4. Won by: 1-1/4; 2; 1-3/4; (1-7.5). Tote: Win Rs 28; Place: 12; 46; 18; Quinella: 497; Shp: 141; Tanala: 2,191. Fav: Gallant Romeo (2). Winner trained by E. Bhungard.				 										4. Hilliard Cup 1,400m: (8-6-7-9) Red Chief (Merchant) 1; Aiberni (Chirstopher) 2; Dashing Chief (Amil) 3; Striesand (Rabani) 4. Won by: 1-1/2; 4; 2-3/4; (1-27.3). Tote: Win Rs 18; Place: 11; 17; 64; Quinella: 42; Shp: 39; Tanala: 712. Fav: Red Chief (8). Winner trained by Daniel D.				 										5. Wiseman Cup 1,600m: (10-12-4-2) Terrificco (Amil) 1; Destiny Dance (Yasin) 2; Followme (Rabani) 3; Sea Legend (Amjad) 4. Won by: 5-3/4; 1; 1-3/4; (1-42). Tote: Win Rs 133; Place: 31; 84; 16; Quinella: 2,082; Shp: 251; Tanala: 69,045. Fav: Arrival (9). Winner trained by Daniel D.				 										6. Nero Handicap 1,200m: (7-4-5-3) Far Hope (Merchant) 1; Rescue Act (Rabani) 2; Venus (M. Reuben) 3; Alborada (Jaiswal) 4. Won by: 1-1/4; 1-3/4; 1-1/4; (1-14.7). Tote: Win Rs 17; Place: 13; 31; 16; Quinella: 109; Shp: 125; Tanala: 498. Fav: Far Hope (7). Winner trained by Daniel D.				 										Jackpot: Rs 2,183; (C) Rs 494.				 										Treble: (i) Rs 635; (ii) Rs 264.
